a multiple marker CLS approach [3].
The buoyancy-driven motion of bubbles is characterized by the Morton number M ‚â°
g¬µ4c (œÅc ‚àí œÅd )/(œÅ2c œÉ 3 ), EoÃàtvoÃàs number Eo ‚â° gd2 (œÅc ‚àí œÅd )/œÉ, density ratio Œ∑œÅ ‚â° œÅc /œÅd , viscosity
